CHANGE mine_turtle_world_project_DESC:1 "在小心地研究了尼玛的生物学构成后，我们的[Root.owner.GetScientistPlural]可以有效地才这些巨星爬行动物的外壳中收获有用的矿物。"
ADD ENLIGHTEN_RADIO:0 "Enlighten the Radiotropic"
CN2 ENLIGHTEN_RADIO:0 "启蒙辐合植物"
ADD ENLIGHTEN_RADIO_DESC:0 "These plants that can live and thrive on worlds with more radiation than atmosphere could be an excellent addition to our empire. But before then, we will need to enhance their minds and teach them thousands of years of progress in a few months."
CN2 ENLIGHTEN_RADIO_DESC:0 "这些可以在极高辐射强度的星球下存活并繁衍兴盛的植物可以作为我们帝国绝佳的补充。不过在此之前，我们需要提升他们的心智并在数月内教会它们我们数千年来的进展。"
ADD GAS_RESTORATION:0 "[From.GetName] Restoration Project"
CN2 GAS_RESTORATION:0 "[From.GetName]恢复计划"
ADD GAS_RESTORATION_DESC:0 "Atoning for your mistakes is a privilege for those with power, and in this scenario, we must atone dearly. The disaster on [From.GetName] was horrifying, and our only hope is that our scientists can reverse the polarity of our deep scanners and potentially reignite the spark of life inside the gas giant."
CN2 GAS_RESTORATION_DESC:0 "为错误赎罪是一项强权者的特权，在此情此景下，我们必须深切地赎罪。[From.GetName]上的灾难令人震愕，而我们唯一的愿望是我们的科学家们能够反转我们深层探测器的极性，寄希望于能以此重新点燃这颗气态巨行星内部的生命之火。"
ADD RESCUE_STORM:0 "Free the [Root.GetName]"
CN2 RESCUE_STORM:0 "释放[Root.GetName]"
ADD RESCUE_STORM_DESC:0 "The [From.GetName] is trapped in a storm on [FromFrom.GetName]. Their only hope may rest in our sending a new ship there, and remotely modulating their shield frequencies."
CN2 RESCUE_STORM_DESC:0 "[From.GetName]被[FromFrom.GetName]上的风暴围困。他们唯一的希望在于我们发射一艘新飞船过去，然后远距离重调制他们的护盾频率。"
ADD STUDY_SLEEPING_CRYSTAL:0 "Study the Strange Asteroid"
CN2 STUDY_SLEEPING_CRYSTAL:0 "研究奇怪的小行星"
ADD STUDY_SLEEPING_CRYSTAL_DESC:0 "[From.GetName] is a strange asteroid that seems to be able to rotate and avoid our mining station through unknown means. We should dispatch a science ship to discover how."
CN2 STUDY_SLEEPING_CRYSTAL_DESC:0 "[From.GetName]是一颗奇怪的小行星，它似乎可以通过未知的方式旋转并躲开我们的开采站。我们需要委派一艘科研船去研究它。"
ADD CRACK_THE_EGG:0 "Crack the Egg"
CN2 CRACK_THE_EGG:0 "破壳"
ADD CRACK_THE_EGG_DESC:0 "The great egg we have discovered in [Solar_System.GetName] is just begging to be dissected. It's an incredible opportunity to get to study such a gargantuan creature's reproductive cycle this close."
CN2 CRACK_THE_EGG_DESC:0 "在[Solar_System.GetName]发现的这颗巨型的蛋刚刚开始产生裂缝。这是一次难以置信的好机会，能够近距离研究这种巨大生命体的繁育循环。"
ADD decision_expand_dayside:0 "Expand Dayside Infrastructure"
CN2 decision_expand_dayside:0 "扩建昼半球基础设施"
ADD decision_expand_dayside_desc:0 "By taking advantage of [Root.GetName]'s unique situation, we can set up solar panels all over the dayside of this world, expanding our energy production immensely."
CN2 decision_expand_dayside_desc:0 "得益于[Root.GetName]的独特情况，我们可以在其昼半球设立无数的太阳能电池板，极大地增强我们的能量产出。"
ADD decision_introduce_chaos:0 "Introduce Chaos"
CN2 decision_introduce_chaos:0 "引入混沌"
ADD decision_introduce_chaos_desc:0 "This world is too perfect for us - our colonists are having mental breakdowns in the streets. Our only real option is to introduce some imperfections."
CN2 decision_introduce_chaos_desc:0 "这颗星球对我们而言简直完美过头了——我们的殖民者在街道上精神崩溃。我们唯一有效的选择是引入一些不完美成分。"
ADD anomaly.6800.name:0 "Target Practice"
CN2 anomaly.6800.name:0 "打靶训练"
ADD anomaly.6800.desc:0 "Our sensors have discovered that the ship remnants on [From.GetName] got there in a peculiar way. The ships seem to have been intentionally driven straight into the asteroid, probably from light-years away, to test the accuracy of the designers' thrusters. As we deep-scan the remains, we pick out one ship in particular, which seems to have reasonably intact propulsion."
CN2 anomaly.6800.desc:0 "我们的敏感器发现了[From.GetName]上的舰船残骸是通过某种罕见的方式抵达那里的。这些舰船似乎是从大约数光年以外故意地径直开向小行星，用以测试设计者的推进器的精确度。在对残骸进行深度扫描时，我们找到了那么一艘具有相当完整推进器的舰船。"
ADD anomaly.6800.a:0 "Recover that thruster!"
CN2 anomaly.6800.a:0 "修复那个推进器！"
ADD anomaly.6800.b:0 "We wont waste those alloys."
CN2 anomaly.6800.b:0 "我们不会浪费那些合金的。"
ADD anomaly.6805.name:0 "Asteroid Sensor Relay"
CN2 anomaly.6805.name:0 "小行星敏感中继器"
ADD anomaly.6805.desc:0 "Hoping to discover rare resources inside [From.GetName], our [Owner.GetScientistPlural] stumbled upon something most unusual. What had appeared to be a simple asteroid was in fact a long-dormant relay station with complex electronics and advanced sensors set up to send signals back to an ancient empire. The impact also has damaged some of the asteroid's internal structure, and we can only extract one system from it."
CN2 anomaly.6805.desc:0 "我们的[Owner.GetScientistPlural]期望在[From.GetName]内部发现稀有资源，结果偶然撞见了一样极其不寻常的东西。这个看起来像是普通小行星的物体事实上是一个长期休眠的中继站，里面有复杂的电子元件和先进的敏感器，用以向某个古老的帝国发送信号。这些撞击也损毁了小行星的一部分内部构造，我们只能从中提取到一个恒星系。"
ADD anomaly.6805.a:0 "Retrieve the Sensors."
CN2 anomaly.6805.a:0 "取回敏感器。"
ADD anomaly.6805.b:0 "Extrapolate their encryption software."
CN2 anomaly.6805.b:0 "破译他们的加密软件。"
ADD anomaly.6810.name:0 "Infestation"
CN2 anomaly.6810.name:0 "感染"
ADD anomaly.6810.desc:0 "We were wrong. The station orbiting [From.GetName] is not uninhabited; instead, it is crawling with giant alien arthropoids! The probes we deployed into the station only returned skittering shadows and large mandibles before signal was lost. Deep scans of the station have also revealed what we postulate to be an incredibly complex databank. To reach this databank, we would have to go through that cluster of many-legged defenders."
CN2 anomaly.6810.desc:0 "我们错了。这座围绕[From.GetName]的空间站并非无人居住；相反，它上面爬满了巨大的外星节肢动物！我们部署进空间站的敏感器在信号中断前只回传了一些行动迅捷的阴影和巨大颚骨的画面。在对空间站进行深度扫描后，我们发现了一处可能是无比复杂的数据库的地方。为了抵达这座数据库，我们需要穿过这些一团团的、有好多腿儿的守护者。"
ADD anomaly.6810.a:0 "Send an away party, giant alien arthropoids are no joke!"
CN2 anomaly.6810.a:0 "送客，巨大的外星节肢动物可不是闹着玩的！"
ADD anomaly.6810.b:0 "It's probably for the best that we leave them alone."
CN2 anomaly.6810.b:0 "也许我们最好还是不要打扰他们。"
ADD anomaly.6810.c:0 "Attempt to contact our fellow arthropoids."
CN2 anomaly.6810.c:0 "尝试与这些节肢动物小伙伴联络。"
ADD anomaly.6810.d:0 "Vent them out."
CN2 anomaly.6810.d:0 "把他们泵出去。"
ADD anomaly.6810.d.tooltip:0 "Use our advance knowledge of habitats to breach the station's atmosphere."
CN2 anomaly.6810.d.tooltip:0 "用我们对居住站的先进知识让空间站的大气层裂一个口子。"
ADD anomaly.6815.name:0 "The Giant Alien Arthropoids"
CN2 anomaly.6815.name:0 "巨大外星节肢动物"
ADD anomaly.6815.desc:0 "Oh, hello there! Sorry about destroying your probe earlier. It's just that we are conducting some very delicate experiments here, and we were worried that outside interference could alter the results - I'm sure you understand. Now, how can we help you?"
CN2 anomaly.6815.desc:0 "噢，你们好！很抱歉之前摧毁了你们的探测器。那只是因为我们在这做一些非常精密的实验，而我们担心一些外在的干扰会影响实验结果——我相信你能理解。那么，我们能帮上什么忙吗？"
ADD anomaly.6815.a:0 "Wait, so you are not a hostile infestation?"
CN2 anomaly.6815.a:0 "慢着，所以你们并不是带有敌意的害虫？"
ADD anomaly.6820.desc:0 "What would ever give you that impression? We are a curator detachment sent here to study this system's unique properties. If you wish to partake of our order's usual offerings, I suggest contacting the primary research lab. I can provide you with a copy of our findings so far."
CN2 anomaly.6820.desc:0 "究竟是什么原因会让你这么想啊？我们是一支策展人分遣队，派驻到这里研究这个恒星系独特的特征。如果你是想分享我们机构通常给予的那些福利，我建议你和我们的主研究实验室联系。我可以提供你一份目前我们在此地所发现的东西的拷贝。"
ADD anomaly.6820.a:0 "Good luck with your experiments."
CN2 anomaly.6820.a:0 "祝你的实验一切顺利。"
ADD anomaly.6825.name:0 "Crystal Growths"
CN2 anomaly.6825.name:0 "生长的水晶"
ADD anomaly.6825.desc.start:0 "The lifeforms living on [From.GetName] were nothing like we expected. Our [owner.GetScientistPlural] report back that the asteroid has crystal growths. These growths have turned out to be self-sustaining and caused by the crystals taking in the ambient radiation of [From.System.GetName] and combining it with the mineral composition of the asteroid."
CN2 anomaly.6825.desc.start:0 "[From.GetName]上生活的生命体形式和我们预想的完全不一样。我们的[owner.GetScientistPlural]汇报到，小行星内有不断生长的水晶。这些生命体利用[From.System.GetName]散发的辐射，并结合小行星内的矿物元素，被证实能够完成自给自足的繁衍生息。"
ADD anomaly.6825.desc.nofood:0 "The crystals themselves are primarily made out of sucrose and are quite brittle."
CN2 anomaly.6825.desc.nofood:0 "这些水晶主要是由蔗糖构成的，十分易碎。"
ADD anomaly.6825.desc.food:0 "The crystals themselves are primarily made out of sucrose and could potentially even be edible."
CN2 anomaly.6825.desc.food:0 "这些水晶主要是由蔗糖构成的，想必具有潜在的食用价值。"
ADD anomaly.6825.b:0 "Edible you say?"
CN2 anomaly.6825.b:0 "啥，你说能吃？"
ADD anomaly.6835.name:0 "Call for Crystals"
CN2 anomaly.6835.name:0 "水晶的呼唤"
ADD anomaly.6835.desc:0 "After eating space-based crystal sugars for a few years now, it has become apparent that our population would like to see it more readily available. Our [Root.GetScientistPlural] have come up with a list of potential candidates where we could construct more crystal farms."
CN2 anomaly.6835.desc:0 "在食用了太空生长的水晶糖数年之后，很明显，我们的人民对这一美食的需求愈发旺盛。我们的[Root.GetScientistPlural]已经列了一份表，上面是能够建造水晶糖农场的潜在候选地。"
ADD anomaly.6835.a:0 "Search for more asteroids to expand the crystal farms."
CN2 anomaly.6835.a:0 "寻找更多的小行星来拓建水晶糖农场。"
ADD anomaly.6835.a.tooltip:0 "Up to §Y3§! random asteroids will now produce §G3§! £food£ food."
CN2 anomaly.6835.a.tooltip:0 "最多§Y3§!个随机小行星将会生产§G3§!£food£食物。"
ADD anomaly.6835.b:0 "Let's not expand the crystal farms."
CN2 anomaly.6835.b:0 "还是不要拓建水晶糖农场了。"
ADD anomaly.6840.name:0 "Too Few Sheep"
CN2 anomaly.6840.name:0 "羊羊太少"
ADD anomaly.6840.desc:0 "[From.GetName] is a peculiar gas giant. Our knowledge of astrophysics tells us that the planet should have a planetary ring, yet it doesn't. The cause of this became apparent after our science ship took a closer look at the intriguing moon. The planet is surrounded by shepherd moons, all incredibly rich in minerals and accumulating more every year. We could blast the moons with precise and controlled explosions and harvest them or keep them inside the ring zone and harvest the space debris they accrue."
CN2 anomaly.6840.desc:0 "[From.GetName]是一颗独特的气态巨行星。我们对天体物理的知识告诉我们，这样的行星应该有一个行星环，然而它并没有。在我们的科研船近距离观察了那颗诡异的卫星之后，这一现象的原因已经十分显然了。这颗星球被一些“牧羊人”卫星所环绕，这些卫星全部拥有富得难以置信的矿物，并且每年还在积累更多。我们可以用精准控制的爆炸爆破这些卫星，然后将它们的矿物一次性收集起来；也可以让它们继续留在环带，持续地收集它们积累下来的太空残骸。"
ADD anomaly.6840.a:0 "We need those minerals now."
CN2 anomaly.6840.a:0 "我们现在就需要那些矿物。"
ADD anomaly.6840.b:0 "Good things come to those who wait."
CN2 anomaly.6840.b:0 "心不急才能喝到热粥。"
ADD anomaly.6845.name:0 "Cascading Catastrophe"
CN2 anomaly.6845.name:0 "连锁灾难"
ADD anomaly.6845.desc:0 "We did indeed discover life on [From.GetName], but by our actions, it has since been eradicated. The microbial creatures which lived in the outer edges of the gas giant's atmosphere reacted poorly to our deep scans. These frequencies caused each creature's cellular structure to resonate - an effect that then cascaded and spread from gas mite to gas mite. Each was rendered inert soon after.\n\nWe are now in orbit over the largest graveyard in the universe."
CN2 anomaly.6845.desc:0 "我们确实在[From.GetName]上发现了生命，但也是因为我们的行动，这一生命已经灭绝了。这些微生生物住在气态巨行星的外层边缘，对于我们的深度扫描表现出了极大的负面反应。扫描的频率同生物的细胞结构产生了共振——这一效应如同瀑布倾斜而下般飞速传开，从一个气态小虫子传播到另一只气态小虫。所有生物都在收到影响之后不久就不再活动了。\n\n我们现在正环绕着全宇宙最大的坟场。"
ADD anomaly.6845.a:0 "Can anything be done?"
CN2 anomaly.6845.a:0 "还有什么能做的吗？"
ADD anomaly.6850.name:0 "Reversing Deep Scan Polarities"
CN2 anomaly.6850.name:0 "反转深度扫描极性"
ADD anomaly.6850.desc:0 "It is done! Miraculously, once our [Owner.GetScientistPlural] installed the proper modifications on our vessel, they were able to recreate the initial cascade. This time the effect was different, and life started springing back up all over [FromFromFrom.GetName] in a great wave."
CN2 anomaly.6850.desc:0 "完成了！如同奇迹一般，当我们的[Owner.GetScientistPlural]对我们的飞船进行了合适的改造之后，它们能够重现最初的瀑布效应。这一次效果不一样，[FromFromFrom.GetName]上的生命体如同一波巨大的浪潮一样又重新涌动了起来。"
ADD anomaly.6850.desc.valuesothers:0 "This process has taught us a lot about the universe but perhaps even more about ourselves."
CN2 anomaly.6850.desc.valuesothers:0 "这一过程教会了我们许多关于宇宙的事情，但更多的可能是关于我们自己的事情。"
ADD anomaly.6850.desc.novaluesothers:0 "In the future we will have to be more careful where we point our scanners."
CN2 anomaly.6850.desc.novaluesothers:0 "在未来，当我们拿出扫描仪的时候，我们必须得更加小心谨慎。"
ADD anomaly.6850.a:0 "Fantastic news!"
CN2 anomaly.6850.a:0 "极好的消息！"
ADD anomaly.6855.name:0 "Caught in the Eye"
CN2 anomaly.6855.name:0 "肉眼捕捉"
ADD anomaly.6855.desc.regular:0 "The last signal received from [Root.GetName] was not much more than garbled static. They had been studying the strange localized storms on [From.GetName] and were sending back incredible preliminary reports. The tempest reacted to the probes being sent in, creating vacuum pockets to avoid them and then slowly seeping back in towards the drones. [Root.GetName] was planning on testing out numerous scanning frequencies at the storm before we lost contact. The science ship seems to have sunken into the gas giant and appears to be dormant."
CN2 anomaly.6855.desc.regular:0 "我们从[Root.GetName]收到的最后一束信号无异于混乱的静电音。他们一直在研究[From.GetName]上奇怪的区域风暴，并且一直发回令人难以置信的前期报告。这股风暴会对发送过去的探测器做出反应，制造出真空口袋来避开它们，再缓慢地往回渗透进探测器。在我们失去联络之前，[Root.GetName]正计划在风暴处测试许多不同的扫描频率。科研船看上去已经沉没到了气态巨行星深处，现在已经陷入了沉寂。"
ADD anomaly.6855.desc.gestalt:0 "The signals from [Root.GetName] were suddenly cut off from the consciousness. The [Owner.GetScientistPlural] do not appear to be dead, just unable to communicate with us. They had been studying the strange localized storms on [From.GetName] and were sending back incredible preliminary reports. The tempest reacted to the probes being sent in, creating vacuum pockets to avoid them and then slowly seeping back in towards the drones. The plan for [Root.GetName] was to test out numerous scanning frequencies at the storm before contact was cut off. The science ship seems to have sunk into the gas giant and now appears dormant."
CN2 anomaly.6855.desc.gestalt:0 "来自[Root.GetName]的信号突然从主脑意识中被切断了。[Owner.GetScientistPlural]看上去并没有死亡，只是无法与我们交流。们一直在研究[From.GetName]上奇怪的区域风暴，并且一直发回令人难以置信的前期报告。这股风暴会对发送过去的探测器做出反应，制造出真空口袋来避开它们，再缓慢地往回渗透进探测器。在联络被切断之前，[Root.GetName]的计划是在风暴处测试许多不同的扫描频率。科研船看上去已经沉没到了气态巨行星深处，现在已经陷入了沉寂。"
ADD anomaly.6855.a:0 "We need to rescue [Root.GetName]!"
CN2 anomaly.6855.a:0 "我们需要营救[Root.GetName]！"
ADD anomaly.6855.b:0 "Wait, [From.GetName] is even MORE interesting now."
CN2 anomaly.6855.b:0 "等等，现在[From.GetName]的局势更—加—有趣了。"
ADD anomaly.6855.b.tooltip:0 "Abandon [Root.GetName] and study the reactions."
CN2 anomaly.6855.b.tooltip:0 "放弃[Root.GetName]，研究反应。"
ADD anomaly.6860.name:0 "Fluctuating Shield Frequencies"
CN2 anomaly.6860.name:0 "涨落的护盾频率"
ADD anomaly.6860.desc:0 "After months of work, our [Owner.GetScientistPlural] finally managed to alternate [FromFrom.GetName] shields in such a way that [FromFromFrom.GetName] tempest released its grip on the marooned ship. Communications with [trapped_in_storm.GetName] was quickly re-established, and incredibly none onboard [FromFrom.GetName] seem to remember their time trapped inside the storm."
CN2 anomaly.6860.desc:0 "在几个月的工作之后，我们的[Owner.GetScientistPlural]终于设法调整[FromFrom.GetName]护盾的工作方式，使得[FromFromFrom.GetName]风暴放开了对落难舰船的钳制。同[trapped_in_storm.GetName]的通讯很快重新建立了起来，十分难以置信的是，[FromFrom.GetName]上没有组员记得他们被风暴困住的这段时间。"
ADD anomaly.6860.a:0 "Back to work."
CN2 anomaly.6860.a:0 "回去工作。"
ADD anomaly.6865.name:0 "Express Mail"
CN2 anomaly.6865.name:0 "快邮"
ADD anomaly.6865.desc:0 "Once [Root.GetName] got close enough to scan the cargo pod it was assumed that the sensors were malfunctioning. The pod is built out of the exact same [Owner.GetBioAlloy] we ourselves use for spacebound structures. The likelihood that some alien beings would come up with this exact mixture is beyond unlikely, yet after recalibrating the scanners the same results appeared.\n\nUpon opening the pod, the only thing greeting us was a collection of documents detailing exactly where we should assign each of our [Owner.GetScientistPlural], and what they should study for 10 years forward."
CN2 anomaly.6865.desc:0 "当[Root.GetName]靠的足够近得以扫描货舱的时候，似乎所有的敏感器都功能失常了。这个舱室使用的[Owner.GetBioAlloy]同我们自己建造太空结构时使用的是完全一样的。这种某些外星生命体发明出了同我们完全一致的复合材料的可能性，根本不可能成立，但在校准了扫描仪之后，我们依然得到了同样的结果。\n\n在打开舱室之后，迎接我们的唯一一样东西是一份文档集，里面详细地阐述了我们应当如何指派我们的每一位[Owner.GetScientistPlural]，以及他们在今后10年应该从事什么研究工作。"
ADD anomaly.6865.a:0 "Send the notes back to [Owner.GetHomeWorldName]."
CN2 anomaly.6865.a:0 "将这些笔记发回[Owner.GetHomeWorldName]。"
ADD anomaly.6865.b:0 "This is too unnerving."
CN2 anomaly.6865.b:0 "这也太让人害怕了。"
ADD anomaly.6870.name:0 "Closing the Loop"
CN2 anomaly.6870.name:0 "关闭循环"
ADD anomaly.6870.desc:0 "After years of uneasy development a rift has appeared above [Root.GetHomeWorldName]. Unnervingly this is the exact same day as the instructions we found before the end. There is only one thing to do: send the notes into the rift and forget this ever happened."
CN2 anomaly.6870.desc:0 "在经过几年不顺坦的发展之后，[Root.GetHomeWorldName]的上方出现了一道裂口。令人心惊胆颤的是，这一天的日期和我们之前发现的指示上面所说的末日前夜是同样的。我们现在只有一件事情可以做了：把那些笔记发射到裂口里面，彻底忘掉这件事情曾经发生过。"
ADD anomaly.6870.a:0 "Let our pasts selves deal with this."
CN2 anomaly.6870.a:0 "让过去的我们自己收拾这个烂摊子吧。"
ADD anomaly.6875.name:0 "Convenient Mining"
CN2 anomaly.6875.name:0 "便利的采矿"
ADD anomaly.6875.desc:0 "The asteroid around [From.GetName] has such a perfectly stable orbit that it's easy to understand why our [Owner.GetScientistPlural] thought it was placed there artificially. Yet, there are no conclusive indications of any propulsion systems or any other artificial marring. The only natural conclusion is that, by some absurdly improbable chance, the asteroid got caught in [From.GetName]'s gravity field. We have also detected some rare crystals on the surface of the asteroid."
CN2 anomaly.6875.desc:0 "[From.GetName]附近小行星的轨道是如此完美无暇地稳定，也不难理解为什么我们的[Owner.GetScientistPlural]会认为它是被人工放置在这个地方了。然而，那里也没有任何推进系统或者其他人工航行的迹象。唯一的自然演化结论是，由于某种几乎荒谬到不可能成真的几率，这颗小行星被[From.GetName]的重力场捕获了。我们在这颗小行星的表面还探测到了几种十分稀有的水晶。"
ADD anomaly.6875.a:0 "How thoughtful."
CN2 anomaly.6875.a:0 "真是贴心啊。"
ADD anomaly.6880.name:0 "Unexplainable Rotations"
CN2 anomaly.6880.name:0 "无法解释的旋转"
ADD anomaly.6880.desc:0 "Just a day after finishing our mining station on the trapped asteroid, the rock abruptly rotated, destroying the mining station. In the process of doing this, even more rare crystals deposits were exposed to our sensors!"
CN2 anomaly.6880.desc:0 "正当我们的采矿站在这颗被捕获的小行星上完工几天之后，这枚岩石突然开始旋转起来，在这个过程中摧毁了采矿站，但同时又有更多的稀有水晶矿藏暴露在了我们的敏感器面前！"
ADD anomaly.6880.a:0 "Build it again!"
CN2 anomaly.6880.a:0 "再建造一遍！"
ADD anomaly.6880.b:0 "Why did it do that?"
CN2 anomaly.6880.b:0 "为什么它要那么做？"
ADD anomaly.6885.name:0 "Annoyed Crystal"
CN2 anomaly.6885.name:0 "发怒的晶体"
ADD anomaly.6885.desc:0 "Warning sirens blared across [Solar_System.GetName] as the massive crystalline beast left the shelter of the asteroid we had been drilling into and extracting crystals from. It seems §Rangry§!."
CN2 anomaly.6885.desc:0 "警报的笛声响彻整个[Solar_System.GetName]，大量的晶化野兽从小行星庇护所里面冲了出来，正是我们在钻孔并打算提取晶体的那颗小行星。它看上去§R生气了§!。"
ADD anomaly.6890.name:0 "Sleeping Crystal Nest"
CN2 anomaly.6890.name:0 "沉睡的晶巢"
ADD anomaly.6890.desc:0 "The trapped asteroid is, in fact, a crystalline being's nest. It is good that we didn't keep digging, for it seems like we agitated the creature hibernating inside. If we do nothing for a while and study it from afar, it should settle down."
CN2 anomaly.6890.desc:0 "这个被捕捉的小行星，实际上，是某种晶态生命体的巢穴。很庆幸我们没有继续挖掘，因为看上去我们似乎激怒了在里面休眠的生物。如果我们什么都不做，只是从远处研究它，这些生物应该会平静下来。"
ADD anomaly.6890.a:0 "What can we learn from it?"
CN2 anomaly.6890.a:0 "我们可以学到什么？"
ADD anomaly.6895.name:0 "Toxic Biological Industry"
CN2 anomaly.6895.name:0 "有毒的生物工业"
ADD anomaly.6895.desc.catano:0 "The life signs observed within the toxic atmosphere of [From.GetName] are giant semi-organic machines! This alien industry seems to have been the cause of the noxious atmosphere on the planet, yet it's still operational. No other life signs remain on the world, and the creators of these machines must have left them running. We can't quite ascertain their purpose yet, but their construction could surely help our understanding of engineering."
CN2 anomaly.6895.desc.catano:0 "我们在[From.GetName]的有毒大气层内观测到的生命信号，是体型庞大的半有机机械体！这个外星工业体似乎正是星球上乌烟瘴气的罪魁祸首，而且它依旧在运转。这个星球上没有其他的生命信号，这些机械体的造物主肯定抛下它们自己跑掉了。我们目前还不能确定它们的意图，但是它们建造的建筑想必能够帮助我们更好地理解工程学。"
ADD anomaly.6895.desc.catayes:0 "The life signs observed within the toxic atmosphere of [From.GetName] are giant semi-organic machines! Like us, it seems like the creators of this facility appreciated a merging of the biological and mechanical. This alien industry appears to have been the cause of the noxious atmosphere on the planet, yet it's still operational. No other life signs remain on the world, and the creators of these machines must have left them running. We can't quite ascertain their purpose yet, but their construction could surely help our understanding of engineering."
CN2 anomaly.6895.desc.catayes:0 "我们在[From.GetName]的有毒大气层内观测到的生命信号，是体型庞大的半有机机械体！正如我们一样，看上去这个设施的创造者也很青睐生物和机械的融合之美。这个外星工业体似乎正是星球上乌烟瘴气的罪魁祸首，而且它依旧在运转。这个星球上没有其他的生命信号，这些机械体的造物主肯定抛下它们自己跑掉了。我们目前还不能确定它们的意图，但是它们建造的建筑想必能够帮助我们更好地理解工程学。"
ADD anomaly.6895.b:0 "Harvest what parts we can."
CN2 anomaly.6895.b:0 "收集我们可以收集的部分。"
ADD anomaly.6895.c:0 "Harvest everything."
CN2 anomaly.6895.c:0 "收集所有。"
ADD anomaly.6895.d:0 "Let the sleeping fools lie."
CN2 anomaly.6895.d:0 "就让沉睡的傻瓜继续躺平吧。"
ADD anomaly.6900.name:0 "Cool Thoughts"
CN2 anomaly.6900.name:0 "冷酷的思绪"
ADD anomaly.6900.desc:0 "We didn't detect life forms below the surface. We detected them in the entire world! The frozen planet is interspersed with micro-thin tubes linked like a rudimentary computer. While the structure is primitive, its gigantic scale means it can probably rival some of [Owner.GetHomeWorldName]'s supercomputers in output. Even now, the computer seems to be active - our [Owner.GetScientistPlural] can interface with it, but since it's so slow, we would only be able to ask it a single question."
CN2 anomaly.6900.desc:0 "我们没有在地表之下检测到生命形式。实际上，我们在整个星球都检测到了生命！这个冰封的星球内部布满了微细的管道，相互连接，就像一台原始的计算机。尽管结构很粗糙，它通天的规模意味着，其算力甚至可以匹敌[Owner.GetHomeWorldName]的某些超级计算机。即使是现在，这台电脑还在活动——我们的[Owner.GetScientistPlural]可以同其互动，但是由于它运转十分缓慢，我们只能询问其一个简单的问题。"
ADD anomaly.6900.a:0 "Can you solve these calculations?"
CN2 anomaly.6900.a:0 "你能够解开这些计算吗？"
ADD anomaly.6900.a.tooltip:0 "Use the world to assist in calculating our current astrophysics dilemmas."
CN2 anomaly.6900.a.tooltip:0 "使用这个星球辅助我们计算当前的天体物理困局。"
ADD anomaly.6900.b:0 "Who made you?"
CN2 anomaly.6900.b:0 "谁制造了你？"
ADD anomaly.6900.c:0 "Who came before us?"
CN2 anomaly.6900.c:0 "我们之前还有谁来过？"
ADD anomaly.6900.d:0 "What are we?"
CN2 anomaly.6900.d:0 "我们是什么？"
ADD anomaly.6900.e:0 "Best to observe it from afar."
CN2 anomaly.6900.e:0 "最好从远处观察。"
ADD anomaly.6905.name:0 "Don't Count Your Planets"
CN2 anomaly.6905.name:0 "不要数行星"
ADD anomaly.6905.desc:0 "Our [Owner.GetScientistPlural] have discovered something rather monstrous. The mountain range they scanned earlier was in actuality the outer membrane of a gigantic egg. It's uncertain what behemoth could lay such an egg and what horror would hatch from it."
CN2 anomaly.6905.desc:0 "我们的[Owner.GetScientistPlural]有了更加惊怖的发现。他们早前扫描到的山脉，实际上是某个巨型蛋的卵壳膜。我们也不知道究竟是什么巨兽诞下了这么一枚蛋，更不知道何等的怖兽会从中孵化出来。"
ADD anomaly.6905.a:0 "Study it from afar."
CN2 anomaly.6905.a:0 "从远处研究。"
ADD anomaly.6905.b:0 "Crack it open!"
CN2 anomaly.6905.b:0 "敲开它！"
ADD anomaly.6905.c:0 "Feast."
CN2 anomaly.6905.c:0 "大餐。"
ADD anomaly.6910.name:0 "Galactic Omelet"
CN2 anomaly.6910.name:0 "星海蛋卷"
ADD anomaly.6910.desc.start:0 "The insides of [FromFromFrom.GetName] were not what we expected. Instead of some infant titanic lifeform, we've simply uncovered genetic slop. The entire planet is filled with genetic material and resources. What all this material would have become is unclear, but our galaxy is probably safer, not knowing."
CN2 anomaly.6910.desc.start:0 "[FromFromFrom.GetName]的内部有什么东西超出我们所料。我们并没有发现什么巨兽生命的幼体，取而代之的只是一团基因浆。整个行星的内部填满了基因物质和资源。全部这些物质最终会变成什么还不明晰，但是如果不打破砂锅问到底，我们的星系可能会更加安全。"
ADD anomaly.6910.desc.hatchling:0 "While similar to the voidspawn our civilization encountered before, this egg would have created something much grander."
CN2 anomaly.6910.desc.hatchling:0 "尽管这个蛋同我们文明之前遭遇到的虚空孶孽很相似，但是它孕育了更加伟大的存在。"
ADD anomaly.6915.name:0 "Gratitude"
CN2 anomaly.6915.name:0 "感恩"
ADD anomaly.6915.desc.regular:0 "§R"IT LIVES! IT LIVES AGAIN! We are nothing but insignificant specks compared to such a creature; what does the ephemeral squabbling between empires matter in the face of such great-"§!\n\nThe last transmission of the [Root.GetName] cuts off there, and when we use our probes to scan the remains of [FromFromFrom.GetName], we find a hollow shell. It seems the creature had little gratitude to show its liberators."
CN2 anomaly.6915.desc.regular:0 "§R“它活了！它又活过来了！同如此至伟的造物相比，我们不过是微不足道的凡尘；面对如此伟大之物，繁星帝国之间的鸡毛琐事又可称几——”§!\n\n[Root.GetName]最后的传输信号在此中断，当我们发送探测器去扫描[FromFromFrom.GetName]残骸的时候，我们只看到了一个空壳。看上去这个生物对自己的解放者并没有多少感激之情。"
ADD anomaly.6915.desc.gestalt:0 "Our [Owner.GetScientistPlural] dispatched to the [Solar_System.GetName] system all reacted in alarm shortly before losing contact with the [Owner.GetBrainName], only telling us that §R"It's loose."§! The last transmission of the [Root.GetName] cuts off as the egg begins to crack open, and when we use our probes to scan the remains of [FromFromFrom.GetName], we find a hollow shell. It seems the creature had little gratitude for its liberator."
CN2 anomaly.6915.desc.gestalt:0 "我们派遣去往[Solar_System.GetName]星系的[Owner.GetScientistPlural]全部拉响了警报，但是没过多久就系数同[Owner.GetBrainName]失去了联系，只告诉了我们§R“它松动了。”§!当蛋壳开始裂开的时候，[Root.GetName]最后的传输信号被切断；当我们发射探测器去扫描[FromFromFrom.GetName]的残骸的时候，我们只看到了一个空壳。看上去这个生物对自己的解放者并没有多少感激之情。"
ADD site_tombworld_weapon_cache:0 "Weapons Cache"
CN2 site_tombworld_weapon_cache:0 "武器贮藏室"
ADD site_tombworld_weapon_cache_desc:0 "A large reinforced cache has been found underneath the broken ground of [From.Planet.GetName]. It's surprisingly intact considering the years it spent buried in a radioactive wasteland."
CN2 site_tombworld_weapon_cache_desc:0 "我们在[From.Planet.GetName]破碎地面的下方发现了一个大型加固贮藏室。考虑到在这样一个充满辐射的废土，还有其被埋葬的年份，我们很惊讶它居然完好无损。"
ADD MESSAGE_HYPERDRIVE_SECURED_TITLE:0 "Hyperdrive Secured"
CN2 MESSAGE_HYPERDRIVE_SECURED_TITLE:0 "超空间引擎担保"
ADD MESSAGE_HYPERDRIVE_SECURED:0 "Our away party managed to pacify the arthropoids and escape with the research."
CN2 MESSAGE_HYPERDRIVE_SECURED:0 "我们的欢送派对计划扫平这些节肢动物并逃离这项研究。"
ADD asteroid_relay_stations:0 "Asteroid Relay Stations"
CN2 asteroid_relay_stations:0 "小行星中继站"
ADD asteroid_relay_stations_desc:0 "This empire has started placing sensors inside asteroids of surrounding systems, granting them increased sensor range."
CN2 asteroid_relay_stations_desc:0 "这个帝国在周边恒星系的小行星内放置了敏感器，增加了它们的探测范围。"
ADD asteroid_encryption:0 "Asteroid Encryption"
CN2 asteroid_encryption:0 "小行星加密"
ADD asteroid_encryption_desc:0 "Using ancient encryption discovered inside an abandoned relay station, this empire protects their secrets."
CN2 asteroid_encryption_desc:0 "使用遗弃的中继站内发现的古代加密技术，这个帝国保护了自己的秘密。"
ADD gas_cascade_sad:0 "Unintended Genocide"
CN2 gas_cascade_sad:0 "无心的物种灭绝"
ADD gas_cascade_sad_desc:0 "This empire is in mourning after accidentally causing the mass extinction of an entire ecosystem."
CN2 gas_cascade_sad_desc:0 "这个帝国在默哀，因为它刚刚意外地酿成了一整个生态系统的大灭绝。"
ADD gas_cascade_happy:0 "Virtuous Relief"
CN2 gas_cascade_happy:0 "道德减负"
ADD gas_cascade_happy_desc:0 "After causing a mass extinction, this empire has set everything to right. The period of mourning has turned into one of celebration."
CN2 gas_cascade_happy_desc:0 "在酿成大灭绝之后，这个帝国将一切拨回了正轨。这段默哀的时期成为了我们的一个节日。"
ADD unexplained_insights:0 "Unexplained Insights"
CN2 unexplained_insights:0 "无法解释的线索"
ADD unexplained_insights_desc:0 "This empire has gotten instructions for how and what they should study."
CN2 unexplained_insights_desc:0 "这个帝国得到了指示，包括他们应该研究什么，怎么研究。"
ADD closed_loop:0 "Closed Loop"
CN2 closed_loop:0 "关闭循环"
ADD closed_loop_desc:0 "This empire have closed the loop and are relived for it."
CN2 closed_loop_desc:0 "这个帝国关闭了循环，并从中解脱。"
ADD asteroid_thrusters:0 "Asteroid Thrusters"
CN2 asteroid_thrusters:0 "小行星推进器"
ADD asteroid_thrusters_desc:0 "Using ancient thrusters built for asteroids, this empire now moves faster."
CN2 asteroid_thrusters_desc:0 "使用为小行星建造的古老推进器，这个帝国现在能够更加迅速地移动。"
ADD not_bio_alloy:0 "alloy"
CN2 not_bio_alloy:0 "合金"
ADD bio_alloy:0 "bio-alloy"
CN2 bio_alloy:0 "生物合金"
ADD terra.15.name:0 "Superfluous Terraforming Equipment"
CN2 terra.15.name:0 "过剩的环境改造设备"
ADD terra.15.desc:0 "After completing the terraforming of §Y[From.GetName]§!, our [Owner.GetTerraformerPlural] have spotted a golden opportunity. The remaining terraforming equipment can potentially be repurposed as infrastructure for the planet."
CN2 terra.15.desc:0 "在完成§Y[From.GetName]§!的环境改造之后，我们的[Owner.GetTerraformerPlural]注意到了一个黄金的机遇。剩下的环境改造设备经过调整改造后可以作为这个行星的基础设施。"
ADD terra.15.a:0 "We could use more housing."
CN2 terra.15.a:0 "我们可以用得上更多的住房。"
ADD terra.15.b:0 "Build some foundries."
CN2 terra.15.b:0 "建造一些合金铸造厂。"
ADD terra.15.c:0 "Expand this world's energy capabilities."
CN2 terra.15.c:0 "拓展这个星球的能量生产力。"
ADD terra.15.c.tooltip:0 "Adds §G2§! §Y$district_generator_plural$§! to Planet"
CN2 terra.15.c.tooltip:0 "这个星球添加§G2§!§Y$district_generator_plural$§!"
ADD terra.15.d:0 "You can never have enough mines."
CN2 terra.15.d:0 "矿是永远不够的。"
ADD terra.15.d.tooltip:0 "Adds §G2§! §Y$district_mining_plural$§! to Planet"
CN2 terra.15.d.tooltip:0 "这个星球添加§G2§!§Y$district_mining_plural$§!"
ADD terra.15.e:0 "More farms for [From.GetName]."
CN2 terra.15.e:0 "[From.GetName]需要更多农场。"
ADD terra.15.e.tooltip:0 "Adds §G2§! §Y$district_farming_plural$§! to Planet"
CN2 terra.15.e.tooltip:0 "这个星球添加§G2§!§Y$district_farming_plural$§!"
ADD terra.15.f:0 "Just scrap the equipment."
CN2 terra.15.f:0 "把这些设备拆解了就好。"
ADD terra.20.name:0 "Engineered Beauty"
CN2 terra.20.name:0 "改造的美景"
ADD terra.20.desc:0 "Terraforming on §Y[From.GetName]§! has finished faster than initially estimated, which has left our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] with time to experiment, and the results are impressive. The planet's natural traits have been enhanced to be both aesthetically pleasing and utilitarian."
CN2 terra.20.desc:0 "环境改造§Y[From.GetName]§!完工得比原先估计的要快，这给了我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]一些额外的时间开展一些实验，实验结果十分引人注目。这颗行星的自然特质得到了强化，既有美学情操，又保证了实用主义。"
ADD terra.20.a:0 "Marvelous!"
CN2 terra.20.a:0 "了不起。"
ADD terra.20.b:0 "Does it have to look so artificial?"
CN2 terra.20.b:0 "它非得看上去这么人工吗？"
ADD terra.25.name:0 "Terraforming Complications"
CN2 terra.25.name:0 "环境改造难题"
ADD terra.25.desc:0 "Our long project on §Y[From.GetName]§! has frustratingly ended in partial success. As the final valleys were undergoing terramorphing, a malfunction occurred in the biomass realigner, leading to the creation of large swaths of §YTerraforming Residue§!. While not dangerous to our colonists, it means that the planet is a bit more cramped for the time being."
CN2 terra.25.desc:0 "我们在§Y[From.GetName]§!上的漫长项目令人沮丧地结束了，只取得了一部分成功。在对最后的几处山谷进行地形变动时，生物质重调器发生了功能异常，导致我们创造出了一大滩§Y环境改造残余物§!。尽管对于殖民者不构成危险，它还是意味着这个星球目前会有一点狭窄。"
ADD terra.25.a:0 "Don't let this happen again."
CN2 terra.25.a:0 "别让这件事再次发生。"
ADD terra.30.name:0 "Learning From Mistakes"
CN2 terra.30.name:0 "以错为鉴"
ADD terra.30.desc:0 "Our [Owner.GetTerraformerPlural] have now cleared the final §YTerraforming Residue§! on §Y[Root.GetName]§!. While the cleanup was painful and quite sticky, it was not all for naught. Analysis of the cause of this issue and the fallout has led to furthering our understanding of terralurgy."
CN2 terra.30.desc:0 "我们的[Owner.GetTerraformerPlural]现在清除了§Y[Root.GetName]§!上的最后一点§Y地形改造残余物§!。尽管清除工作十分痛苦、还黏黏糊糊，但这一切并非没有价值。对造成这一事故的原因和后果进行分析，使我们对地形学有了更加深远的理解。"
ADD terra.30.a:0 "At least some good has come of it."
CN2 terra.30.a:0 "好歹还是有点好处的。"
ADD terra.35.name:0 "[Root.GetHomeWorldName] II"
CN2 terra.35.name:0 "[Root.GetHomeWorldName]二号"
ADD terra.35.desc:0 "We have not only succeeded in terraforming §Y[From.GetName]§!, but we have done something even better. During the final stretch of the process, our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] managed to make it a perfect home for our local fauna, creating a [From.GetPlanetMoon] eerily similar to [Root.GetHomeWorldName]. All our local plant life is there but none of the familiar terrain."
CN2 terra.35.desc:0 "我们不仅成功地对§Y[From.GetName]§!进行了环境改造，我们还做得更加好了。在定稿阶段的最后，我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]设法想让这个星球成为我们本土动物群的完美家园，创造一个同[Root.GetHomeWorldName]及其相似的[From.GetPlanetMoon]。我们的所有本土植物也会移植到那里去，只是地形会不太一样。"
ADD terra.35.a:0 "This [From.GetPlanetMoon] shall be known as [Root.GetHomeWorldName] II"
CN2 terra.35.a:0 "这个[From.GetPlanetMoon]应该作为[Root.GetHomeWorldName]二号被人所知"
ADD terra.35.a.tooltip:0 "Sets the name of §Y[From.GetName]§! to §Y$terra.35.name$§!"
CN2 terra.35.a.tooltip:0 "将§Y[From.GetName]§!的名字改为§Y$terra.35.name$§!"
ADD terra.35.b:0 "A fortuitous development."
CN2 terra.35.b:0 "一次幸运的发展。"
ADD terra.40.name:0 "A Planetary Gambit"
CN2 terra.40.name:0 "行星策略"
ADD terra.40.desc:0 "A unique situation has occurred on §Y[From.GetName]§! just as the terraforming efforts are winding down. Our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] have discovered that it's possible to tidally lock the [From.GetPlanetMoon]. This occurring naturally can be quite a detriment to a colony. However, doing it during the terraforming process could allow us to exploit the endless solar hours the dayside will receive and generate an obscene amount of energy. We would still have to make a concentrated effort to set up the rest of our industry and housing on the twilight and night side."
CN2 terra.40.desc:0 "正当§Y[From.GetName]§!的环境改造工程即将收尾之时，一个独特的情况发生了。我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]发现，我们有可能将这个[From.GetPlanetMoon]变为潮汐锁定。这样的现象如果自然发生了，可能会对殖民地造成危害。然而，如果是在环境改造的过程中这么做，我们就能充分利用昼半球无穷无尽的太阳时长，产出极其丰富的能量。我们当然也要制定一个集中计划，将我们剩余的工业园区和住房布置在夜半球或晨昏线地区。"
ADD terra.40.a:0 "Set the [From.GetPlanetMoon] spinning again, the risk is too great."
CN2 terra.40.a:0 "让[From.GetPlanetMoon]再次转起来，这么做风险太大了。"
ADD terra.40.b:0 "Do it."
CN2 terra.40.b:0 "就这么做。"
ADD terra.40.b.tooltip:0 "Unlocks a special §Yplanetary decision§! to unlock this [From.GetPlanetMoon]'s full potential."
CN2 terra.40.b.tooltip:0 "解锁一项特殊的§Y行星决议§!，能够彻底解锁这个[From.GetPlanetMoon]的全部潜势。"
ADD terra.45.name:0 "Excess to Success"
CN2 terra.45.name:0 "成功过头"
ADD terra.45.desc:0 "As the terraforming of §Y[From.GetName]§! is settling down, we discover that the project has put us in an unanticipated situation. We did not need as many resources as we initially set aside to finish this project, and now we have the chance to add-on one additional feature to the [From.GetPlanetMoon]. Our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] have presented us with three different options."
CN2 terra.45.desc:0 "随着§Y[From.GetName]§!环境改造完工，我们发现这一工程使我们处在了一个始料未及的情况。我们实际上需要的资源，并没有我们最初立项的时候预计完成项目所需要的那么多，现在我们有机会为这个[From.GetPlanetMoon]增添一项额外的特征。我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]呈递给了我们三个不同的选项。"
ADD terra.45.a:0 "We could use more $district_generator_plural$."
CN2 terra.45.a:0 "我们可以使用更多的$district_generator_plural$。"
ADD terra.45.b:0 "See if we can't develop more space for $district_mining_plural$."
CN2 terra.45.b:0 "看看我们是不是能够为$district_mining_plural$提供更多空间。"
ADD terra.45.c:0 "This world could use more $district_farming_plural$."
CN2 terra.45.c:0 "这个星球用得上更多的$district_farming_plural$。"
ADD terra.50.name:0 "Oneness"
CN2 terra.50.name:0 "真一"
ADD terra.50.desc:0 "While turning §Y[From.GetName]§! into [This.GetAAnPlanetClass] [This.GetClassAdj] world, the [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] managed to link not only the local fauna to the mind but, through freak mutations when exposed to the terraforming gasses, link the mind to the world itself. The collective now has the opportunity to become whole in a truer sense than before."
CN2 terra.50.desc:0 "在将§Y[From.GetName]§!转变为[This.GetAAnPlanetClass][This.GetClassAdj]星球的过程中，[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]筹划着不仅将当地动物群连接到主脑，还想将这个星球本身也连接到主脑，尽管有点担心暴露在环境改造气体中有可能诱发突变。蜂群现在有机会在更加真实的感知下，变得前所未有地完整。"
ADD terra.50.a:0 "Yes, the mind wills it."
CN2 terra.50.a:0 "是的，这是主脑的意志。"
ADD terra.50.b:0 "No, this is not the intention for this world."
CN2 terra.50.b:0 "不，这不是这个星球的意图。"
ADD terra.55.name:0 "Perfect Organization"
CN2 terra.55.name:0 "完美的组织"
ADD terra.55.desc:0 "Surpassing nature is not something new for this collective. During the terraforming process of §Y[From.GetName]§!, every hill was considered, and every piece of fauna was strategically placed. The [From.GetPlanetMoon] has now ended up being a perfectly organized logistical paradise for our [Root.GetUnitDronePlural] to produce for the collective."
CN2 terra.55.desc:0 "对于蜂群来说，超越自然不是什么新鲜事。在对§Y[From.GetName]§!进行地形改造的过程中，每一座山峦都经过了考量，每一片动物群的放置都经过了战略推演。这个[From.GetPlanetMoon]现在变成了一处组织完美的后勤天堂，方便我们的[Root.GetUnitDronePlural]为蜂群整体的建设添砖加瓦。"
ADD terra.55.a:0 "How pleasing."
CN2 terra.55.a:0 "真是可喜可贺。"
ADD terra.65.name:0 "A Helpful Blemish"
CN2 terra.65.name:0 "有所帮助的瑕疵"
ADD terra.65.desc:0 "What our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] first took for a nasty gas pocket on §Y[From.GetName]§! has turned out to be a blessing! The toxic fumes it was releasing are an unrefined version of §YExotic Gas§!. With this new natural resource, the energy required to introduce an atmosphere to the [From.GetPlanetMoon] has drastically decreased, and we can harvest the gas for years to come!"
CN2 terra.65.desc:0 "我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]一开始以为某块地只是§Y[From.GetName]§!上的一个臭气袋子，结果没想到那里竟是一块福地！它喷发出来的有毒气体实际上是未经精炼的§Y异星天然气§!。有了这处全新的自然资源，为这个[From.GetPlanetMoon]引入大气层所需的能源巨幅下降了，我们还可以在接下来的很多年采集这里的天然气！"
ADD terra.65.a:0 "Excellent."
CN2 terra.65.a:0 "棒极了。"
ADD terra.70.name:0 "Unexpected Mutations"
CN2 terra.70.name:0 "未曾预料的突变"
ADD terra.70.desc:0 "Our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] have good news and bad news for us about §Y[From.GetName]§!. The good news is that the terraforming process went swimmingly, and we have a beautiful Gaia World. The bad news is that everyone living on the [From.GetPlanetMoon] was exposed to the terraforming gasses and now can't live on non-Gaia Worlds. These Gaia-trapped inhabitants have surprisingly been showing an increase in their productivity while on the Gaia World. Far better than workers that weren't affected by the gas that migrated there later."
CN2 terra.70.desc:0 "我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]就§Y[From.GetName]§!上的情况即带来了好消息，也带来了坏消息。好消息是环境改造进程十分的顺利，我们有了一处美轮美奂的盖亚星球。坏消息是，所有住在这个[From.GetPlanetMoon]上的人都暴露在了环境改造气体中，已经不能适应非盖亚星球的环境了。这些“囿于盖亚”的居民在盖亚星球上生活时，展现出了惊人的生产力提升。相比于没有受到环境改造气体影响、在改造之后才过去的移民，这些居民的表现要好得不知道到哪里去了。"
ADD terra.70.a:0 "At least they don't seem to be uncomfortable."
CN2 terra.70.a:0 "至少他们看上去没有感到不舒服。"
ADD terra.75.name:0 "Paradise is a Place on [From.GetName]"
CN2 terra.75.name:0 "[From.GetName]此处便是天堂"
ADD terra.75.desc_regular:0 "Amongst our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] assigned to §Y[From.GetName]§!, there seem to have been followers of an ancient sect from [Root.GetHomeWorldName] among them. These [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] believe that there is a paradise for our people, and instead of looking for it, they have now created it. [From.GetName] has now been turned into a [From.GetPlanetMoon] of the blessed, looking like an illustration manifested from the pages of our ancient history."
CN2 terra.75.desc_regular:0 "在我们派往§Y[From.GetName]§!的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]之中，似乎有部分人是某个[Root.GetHomeWorldName]上古老宗派的追随者。这些[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]相信寰宇之中有一处留给我们人民的天堂，结果他们选择不去寻找，而是亲自去创造这处天堂。[From.GetName]现在被转变成了一处被赐福的[From.GetPlanetMoon]，宛如从我们古老历史的宗卷中显现出来的图景。"
ADD terra.75.desc_spirit:0 "Our terraformers have outdone any of their previous work! Throughout [Root.GetName], history there have always been myths and legends about a blessed land for our people, a paradise. When we set out to the stars and didn't find the Land of Bliss, a project to make it a reality was started by our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural]. Now the awe-inspiring horizons of §Y[From.GetName]§! stretch before us, and we know that we have made our own paradise."
CN2 terra.75.desc_spirit:0 "我们的环境改造工作者完成了前所未有的功绩！阅尽整个[Root.GetName]的历史，总有一桩神话或传说流传下来，讲述许诺给我们人民的赐福之地——一处天堂。当我们驶向繁星却无处寻觅这处福地时，我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]启动了一项计划，要亲自将这个传说化为现实。现在，§Y[From.GetName]§!的地平线在我们面前向远方延伸，人人肃然起敬，心知我们亲手缔造了属于自己的天堂。"
ADD terra.75.a:0 "It's beautiful."
CN2 terra.75.a:0 "美不胜收。"
ADD terra.75.b:0 "It's just a normal Gaia World?"
CN2 terra.75.b:0 "它只是个普通的盖亚星球吧？"
ADD terra.80.name:0 "Radioactive Flora"
CN2 terra.80.name:0 "辐射植物"
ADD terra.80.desc:0 "While cleaning out the radiation in §Y[From.GetName]'s§! atmosphere and soil, our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] had to call in our xenobiologists. They had found a species that seemed to thrive off the radiation and was now wilting. Even more curious, this species appears to be presapient and on the cusp of achieving sentience. Now, as the final soil scrubbers are approaching, we have to decide what to do with this new life."
CN2 terra.80.desc:0 "在清除§Y[From.GetName]§!大气层和土壤中的辐射的过程中，我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]不得不求助于我们的异星生物学家。他们发现了一个物种，依靠辐射繁衍生息，而现在正在枯萎。更令人惊奇的是，这个物种看上去还处于未开智状态，但将将就要进化出智能了。现在，随着最后一处泥土即将冲刷干净，我们必须决定如何处置这个新生命。"
ADD terra.80.a:0 "We have destroyed their habitat, now we have to preserve them."
CN2 terra.80.a:0 "我们毁掉了它们的栖息地，现在我们应当保护它们。"
ADD terra.80.a.tooltip:0 "4 presapient §YRadiotrophic £pops£ pops§! will be added to the [This.GetName]."
CN2 terra.80.a.tooltip:0 "4个未开智的§Y辐射合成£pops£人口§!会添加至[This.GetName]。"
ADD terra.80.b:0 "Why not let them join us?"
CN2 terra.80.b:0 "为什么不让它们加入我们？"
ADD terra.80.c.indifferent:0 "Harvest their genetic material."
CN2 terra.80.c.indifferent:0 "收集它们的基因物质。"
ADD terra.80.c.xenophile:0 "Study their biology."
CN2 terra.80.c.xenophile:0 "研究它们的生物学。"
ADD terra.80.c.cantuse:0 "While not applicable to us, their genetical material could be useful."
CN2 terra.80.c.cantuse:0 "尽管无法应用到我们身上，但它们的基因物质可能有用。"
ADD terra.80.c.tooltip:0 "Unlocks the §Y$trait_plantoid_radiotrophic$§! trait for genemodding."
CN2 terra.80.c.tooltip:0 "解锁§Y$trait_plantoid_radiotrophic$§!特质用于基因修饰。"
ADD terra.80.d:0 "Why are we even bothering with this weed. Finish the terraforming."
CN2 terra.80.d:0 "我们何苦要担忧这些杂草呢。完成环境改造。"
ADD terra.85.name:0 "A Radiating Reception"
CN2 terra.85.name:0 "辐光四溢的招待会"
ADD terra.85.desc:0 "Having spent years acclimating and adjusting the radiotropic plants found on §Y[FromFromFrom.GetName]§!, we now are ready to allow them into our society. While an incredibly young species, they seem to excel in harvesting energy."
CN2 terra.85.desc:0 "在花费数年调整这些我们在§Y[FromFromFrom.GetName]§!上发现的辐射合成植物，并且使其适应环境之后，我们现在可以将他们纳入我们的社会了。尽管这个物种还出人意料地年轻，但是他们看上去非常擅长收集能量。"
ADD terra.85.a:0 "Welcome!"
CN2 terra.85.a:0 "欢迎！"
ADD terra.85.a.tooltip:0 "6 §YRadiotrophic £pops£ pops§! will be added to our Empire."
CN2 terra.85.a.tooltip:0 "6§Y辐射合成£pops£人口§!加入我们的帝国。"
ADD terra.90.name:0 "Weapons Cache"
CN2 terra.90.name:0 "武器贮藏室"
ADD terra.90.desc:0 "Restoring a Tomb World is always hard work and often very repetitive: section off an area, clear out any rubble, replace the soil, purify any remaining water, and add new fauna. As the terraforming process on §Y[From.GetName]§! was winding to a close, our [Root.GetTerraformerPlural] discovered a sizeable underground metal container, and based on its fortifications, it is assumed that this is a weapons cache."
CN2 terra.90.desc:0 "恢复一个死寂星球是一项艰苦的工作，而且十分单调重复：隔绝一块区域，清理所有的卵石，替换土地，净化任何残留的水源，添加新的动物。随着§Y[From.GetName]§!的环境改造进程逐渐扫尾，我们的[Root.GetTerraformerPlural]发现了一个规模可观的地下金属容器，根据其防御工事，我们假定这是一个武器库。"
ADD terra.90.a:0 "Curious."
CN2 terra.90.a:0 "令人好奇。"
ADD terra.95.name:0 "Bringing the Past to Light"
CN2 terra.95.name:0 "揭开尘封的过去"
ADD terra.95.desc:0 "The cache on [From.Planet.GetName] was not easy to unearth, as it was buried deep below the ruined city in which it was discovered. The excavation effort was further slowed by the caution required to avoid setting off whatever is stored in the container. Now the structure stands before us and is ready to for investigation. Complex alien script is carved into the sides of the cache that might hint at its content."
CN2 terra.95.desc:0 "[From.Planet.GetName]的贮藏室并不好挖掘，因为它的发现地点被深深地埋在了城市废墟之下。又因为不管容器里面储藏着什么，我们都被要求谨慎行事避免将其误触发，发掘进度被进一步地拖慢了。现在这栋建筑矗立在我们的面前，等待我们随时开始调查。复杂的外星文字被刻在贮藏室的两侧，或许能提示我们里面有什么内容物。"
ADD terra.100.name:0 "The Armory"
CN2 terra.100.name:0 "军械库"
ADD terra.100.desc:0 "Our [Owner.GetLinguists] have finished translating the alien inscriptions and have discovered a warning engraved into the cache. §Y"Do not under any circumstances allow any government to have access to this armory during wartime!"§!\n\nWhatever weapon was stored here was too destructive even for a civilization that was capable of reducing themselves to ash. All that is left is to carefully open the armory and claim our prize."
CN2 terra.100.desc:0 "我们的[Owner.GetLinguists]完成了翻译外星人的铭文，发现贮藏室外刻着一个警示。§Y“在战争时期，任何情况下，都不允许任何政府进入这座军械库！”§!\n\n无论这里面储存着什么武器，那对于一整个文明都具有足够的毁灭性，能够将他们化成灰。我们剩下的工作就是小心地打开这座军械库，然后拿到我们的奖励。"
ADD terra.105.name:0 "Mistranslations"
CN2 terra.105.name:0 "翻译错误"
ADD terra.105.desc.generic:0 "It seems like our [Owner.GetLinguists] mistranslated the word 'library' as 'armory'. We had assumed the incorrect meaning of 'source of power', which was only apparent after opening the cache and being greeted by further xeno script. §Y"If you are reading this, that means that we survived the war and are now ready to rebuild. I spent many long months creating this library while our world's situation worsened, accompanied by my friend and faithful companion. But since you are reading this, that means that someone did survive, so please take part in your heritage. All the cultural works of our people my friend and I could gather are collected here, and let the first you see be a representation of my dearest friend."§!\n\nThe remains of a bipedal mammal and a metal statue of a four-legged long-snouted animal stands under the plaque."
CN2 terra.105.desc.generic:0 "似乎是我们的[Owner.GetLinguists]将“图书馆”错误翻译成了“军械库”。我们一直对“权力的来源”一词存在错误的理解，直到我们打开了贮藏室，看到了更多的外星文本。§Y“如果你在读这一段，那说明我们从战争中存活了下来，现在准备开始重建。当我们星球的局势变得愈发恶化的时候，我花费了许多个月份创建这座图书馆，我的朋友和我忠实的同事一直陪伴左右。但既然你在读这一段，那说明我们中的某人幸存了下来，因此请好好接受这一份遗产。我和我的朋友收集到的，所有有关我们人民文化的成果，都集中在这里。你们第一个看见这个的人，将成为我最亲爱的朋友的象征。”§!\n\n在饰板的下面，是一个双足哺乳动物的遗体，以及一个四足长鼻子动物的金属雕像。"
ADD terra.105.desc.earth:0 "It seems like our [Owner.GetLinguists] mistranslated the word 'library' as 'armory'. We had assumed the incorrect meaning of 'source of power', which was only apparent after opening the cache and being greeted by further xeno script. §Y"If you are reading this, that means that we survived the war and are now ready to rebuild. I spent many long months creating this library while our world's situation worsened, accompanied by my friend and faithful companion Walter. But since you are reading this, that means that someone did survive, so please take part in your heritage. All the cultural works of our people Walter and I could gather are collected here, and let the first you see be a representation of my dearest friend."§!\n\nThe remains of a bipedal mammal and a metal statue of a four-legged long-snouted animal stands under the plaque."
CN2 terra.105.desc.earth:0 "似乎是我们的[Owner.GetLinguists]将“图书馆”错误翻译成了“军械库”。我们一直对“权力的来源”一词存在错误的理解，直到我们打开了贮藏室，看到了更多的外星文本。§Y“如果你在读这一段，那说明我们从战争中存活了下来，现在准备开始重建。当我们星球的局势变得愈发恶化的时候，我花费了许多个月份创建这座图书馆，我的朋友和我忠实的同事——沃尔特——一直陪伴左右。但既然你在读这一段，那说明我们中的某人幸存了下来，因此请好好接受这一份遗产。我和沃尔特收集到的，所有有关我们人民文化的成果，都集中在这里。你们第一个看见这个的人，将成为我最亲爱的朋友的象征。”§!\n\n在饰板的下面，是一个双足哺乳动物的遗体，以及一个四足长鼻子动物的金属雕像。"
ADD terra.105.a:0 "Pet the statue."
CN2 terra.105.a:0 "抚摸雕像。"
ADD terra.105.b:0 "Catalogue the alien media."
CN2 terra.105.b:0 "将外星媒体登记。"
ADD terra.105.c:0 "We were promised weapons, melt the library and statue down and use it for missiles."
CN2 terra.105.c:0 "说好给我们武器的，把图书馆和雕像融化掉用来造导弹。"
ADD d_terraforming_blocker:0 "£blocker£ Terraforming Residue"
CN2 d_terraforming_blocker:0 "£blocker£环境改造残骸"
ADD d_terraforming_blocker_desc:0 "The results of a partially successful terraforming project have created areas of strange biological abominations."
CN2 d_terraforming_blocker_desc:0 "部分成功的环境改造工程，其结果是在很多区域创造了奇怪的生物遗骸。"
ADD d_dayside_farm:0 "Dayside Solar Farm"
CN2 d_dayside_farm:0 "昼半球农场"
ADD d_dayside_farm_desc:0 "This world has all its solar power set up on the dayside of its tidally locked hemispheres, granting it access to an unlimited amount of solar hours."
CN2 d_dayside_farm_desc:0 "这个星球被潮汐锁定，所有的太阳能都投射在了昼半球，使得这片区域拥有无限的昼时。"
ADD d_radiotrophic_preserve:0 "Radiotrophic Preserve"
CN2 d_radiotrophic_preserve:0 "辐射合成保护区"
ADD d_radiotrophic_preserve_desc:0 "An isolated area filled with low pressure and a very radioactive atmosphere keeps the natives of this world alive."
CN2 d_radiotrophic_preserve_desc:0 "一片隔离区，充满低气压和充满辐射的大气，能够让这颗星球的当地土著物种存活。"
CHANGE fumongus_monitor_pops_desc:0 "我们已经成功地利用本地真菌网络来监控星球上的殖民者。"
ADD engineered_nature:0 "Engineered Nature"
CN2 engineered_nature:0 "改造的自然"
ADD engineered_nature_desc:0 "This [Root.GetPlanetMoon] has been engineered to provide both form and function to its inhabitants."
CN2 engineered_nature_desc:0 "这个[Root.GetPlanetMoon]被工程改造，为其居民提供形态和功能。"
ADD second_home:0 "Second Home"
CN2 second_home:0 "第二家园"
ADD second_home_desc:0 "This [Root.GetPlanetMoon] bears an uncanny resemblance to its creator's homeworld."
CN2 second_home_desc:0 "这颗[Root.GetPlanetMoon]看上去同其创造者的母星有着惊世骇俗的相似性。"
ADD intentionally_tidally_locked:0 "Intentionally Tidally Locked"
CN2 intentionally_tidally_locked:0 "有意的潮汐锁定"
ADD intentionally_tidally_locked_desc:0 "During the terraforming process, this world was intentionally left tidally locked to take advantage of the amount of energy that could potentially be gathered on the dayside."
CN2 intentionally_tidally_locked_desc:0 "在环境改造的过程中，这个星球被有意地改造成为了潮汐锁定的状态，使得人们能够充分利用在向阳面收集的能量。"
